{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"06c8eed930","title":"大字报——青春血泪","origin":"《“鸣”、“放”选集（一）》（中共山西省委整风办公室编，1957年8月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dc43f1ac27","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":5,"articleId":"06c8eed930"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"79af059482","name":"山西师范学院"},{"id":"c5f6c838f0","name":"尹剑秋"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e5f8a73942","type":"title","text":"大字报——青春血泪","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"},{"id":"86ce821d79","type":"authors","text":"山西师范学院尹剑秋","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"},{"id":"8bdb955723","type":"subtitle","text":"青春血泪","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"},{"id":"0a4718f37a","type":"paragraph","text":"自觉的不自觉的披着马列主义外衣的魔鬼们：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"},{"id":"f5a87f3151","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的青春，我们善良的心，在你们残酷蹂躏下，早已模糊不清。今天的正义使它凝成了血泪与语言，我们哭诉一句语言，一行泪，难道我们永远哭诉，不！在最肮脏的地方，我们要暴风骤雨，只有这样才能洗尽这美好大地上的尘土。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"},{"id":"6643d16fbb","type":"paragraph","text":" 山西师范学院  尹剑秋1957年6月5日晚2时","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"},{"id":"05569fd4bf","type":"subtitle","text":"呼  吁","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"},{"id":"eefde2471e","type":"paragraph","text":"真理正义，人类的良心，被暴力蹂躏，用被迫害人们的血和泪，写成了苏副院长的总结（肃反运动的总结）“成绩是主要的”，我们呼吁支持我们的正义要求，追查王中青应负的责任！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"},{"id":"1fa39ddc7c","type":"paragraph","text":" 山西师范学院  ×××","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930"}],"page":{"id":"5331dcbbfc","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"06c8eed930","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}